To ensure Third Party quotes/orders are processed correctly, we have outlined the steps below: 

1. Partner contacts sales requesting a quote that includes the Connections Program discount. 

2. Sales representative forwards request to connections@mathworks.com for approval. 

3. If approved, the Connections Program team will reply and provide you with a approval code. Please make note of this number. The approval code is used to track this request, and it is for a one-time use only. It cannot be reused for multiple discount requests/approvals. 

